atc_geom.F
               - подпрограмма геометрии черенковских счетчиков
atc_card.F
               - Subr. reads card for aerogel counters simulation.
                 Добавлена возможность расширенного подключения/отключения геометрии АЧС.
atc_amp.F
	       - Determines average number of photo-electrons in counters
atc_hits.F
               - Defines hits of aerogel threshold counterts
atc_digi.F
               - Preparation of common-block with data from ATC for writing
atcrawhits.inc
               - This common block contains raw information about hits in ATC


